---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Team — SPHERE Research and Advocacy"
  description="Meet the team behind SPHERE: dedicated professionals working to advance human rights, digital policy, and community empowerment in Sri Lanka."
>
  <main class="page page-animate">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section section--hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <div class="hero__eyebrow" style="text-align: center;">Our Team</div>
          <h1 class="hero__title text-balance" style="text-align: center;">
            Lean core, networked expertise
          </h1>
          <p class="hero__desc" style="text-align: center; max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto 24px;">
            SPHERE is powered by a dedicated team of advocates, researchers, and organizers
            working collaboratively to advance human rights and democratic participation in Sri Lanka.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Team -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section__title" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
          Leadership Team
        </h2>
        <p class="section__kicker" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
          Cross-functional co-founders guiding programs and partnerships
        </p>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="/team/placeholder_1.png"
              alt="Sherene Dias"
              class="team-card__image"
            />
            <div class="team-card__content">
              <h3 class="team-card__name">Sherene Dias</h3>
              <div class="team-card__role">Finance & Technology</div>
              <p class="team-card__bio">
                Sherene is an Information Systems undergraduate at the University of Colombo School of Computing and an AAT Passed Finalist reading for Chartered Accountancy. With three years of professional audit experience, she specializes in the intersection of finance and technology. She is a dedicated advocate for human rights, committed to promoting transparency and accountability in business.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="/team/placeholder_2.png"
              alt="Pubudu Viduranga"
              class="team-card__image"
            />
            <div class="team-card__content">
              <h3 class="team-card__name">Pubudu Viduranga</h3>
              <div class="team-card__role">Community Mobilization & Youth Empowerment</div>
              <p class="team-card__bio">
                Pubudu is a Marketing Executive and Student Counsellor at Asian International Academy, holding a Master’s in Sociology and a degree in Mass Media. With a strong background in child rights advocacy and social research, he specializes in community mobilization and youth empowerment. He is passionate about driving social impact through effective communication and development initiatives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="/team_member_3_1770090760464.png"
              alt="Team Member"
              class="team-card__image"
            />
            <div class="team-card__content">
              <h3 class="team-card__name">Nalini Silva</h3>
              <div class="team-card__role">Director of Programs & Training</div>
              <p class="team-card__bio">
                Oversees training initiatives and community engagement programs. Experienced
                in grassroots organizing and capacity-building across Sri Lanka.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Organizational Structure -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.5));">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section__title" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
          Organizational Structure
        </h2>
        <p class="section__kicker" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
          Strategic oversight with an independent majority
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <div class="icon-box__icon">🏛️</div>
            <div class="icon-box__content">
              <h3>Board of Directors</h3>
              <p>
                Provides strategic oversight and governance with an independent majority.
                Ensures accountability, transparency, and alignment with our mission and values.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-box">
            <div class="icon-box__icon">👥</div>
            <div class="icon-box__content">
              <h3>Core Team</h3>
              <p>
                Lean staff across advocacy, research, training, and operations. Day-to-day
                program implementation and strategic interventions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-box">
            <div class="icon-box__icon">🎯</div>
            <div class="icon-box__content">
              <h3>Advisory Board</h3>
              <p>
                Subject-matter experts and legal/technical consultants engaged as needed.
                Provides specialized knowledge in digital rights, law, and policy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-box">
            <div class="icon-box__icon">🌱</div>
            <div class="icon-box__content">
              <h3>Grassroots Network</h3>
              <p>
                Community partners, local organizers, and field trainers across Sri Lanka.
                Ensures our work stays rooted in community needs and realities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How We Work -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section__title" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
          How We Work
        </h2>
        <p class="section__kicker" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
          Our approach and values in action
        </p>
        <div class="cards cards--three">
          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title">Evidence-First</h3>
            <p class="card__desc">
              We base our work on rigorous research, legal analysis, and documented evidence.
              Every intervention is grounded in facts and data.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title">Non-Partisan</h3>
            <p class="card__desc">
              We work across political divides, focusing on principles rather than parties.
              Our advocacy serves all Sri Lankans regardless of political affiliation.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title">Collaborative</h3>
            <p class="card__desc">
              We partner with civil society organizations, media, legal experts, and
              international allies to amplify our impact.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Join the Team -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section__title">Join the Movement</h2>
            <p class="section__kicker">Partners, volunteers, and advisors welcome</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
              <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                SPHERE is always looking for talented individuals who share our commitment to
                human rights, digital policy, and democratic participation.
              </p>
              <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                Whether you're interested in joining as a staff member, volunteer, pro-bono
                advisor, or partner organization, we'd love to hear from you.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="display: grid; gap: 16px;">
            <div>
              <h3 class="card__title">Opportunities</h3>
              <p class="card__desc">
                We seek expertise in advocacy, legal research, policy analysis, community
                organizing, communications, and digital security.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="card__title">Contact Us</h3>
              <p class="card__desc">
                Send your expression of interest to
                <a href="mailto:hello@sphereresearch.org" class="link">
                  hello@sphereresearch.org
                </a>
                with a brief description of your background and how you'd like to contribute.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-row">
              <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
              <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/about">Learn more about SPHERE</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
